{"tid":652803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國keep 嬴!]夏威夷火山爆發 1萬名居民緊急疏散","createTime":"2018-05-04T06:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:43:42.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10ed02fb7c32429999e1307d2621bf8fba66a7b6","tid":652803,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58150127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58150127&d=VW6EldCff5cYGF6oeE%2BgtTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=41254d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58150127&h=84541d51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58150127</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;再嬴&quot;同&quot;又嬴&quot;已經侮辱緊強國要用 keep 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【更新火山已爆發】<br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷基拉韋厄火山（Kilauea Volcano），周三早上錄得50次小型地震後爆發，溶岩流向民居，夏威夷下令受影響區域多達<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1萬名民眾</span>緊急疏散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美聯社報道，火熱的溶岩在「Leilani Estates」住宅區裂縫流出，「Mohala Street」更已被溶岩覆蓋，下令附近民眾緊急疏散。<br />\n觀察站所屬的美國地質堪探局，周三派出兩批地面工作人員，前往現場安裝新監察儀器。夏威夷教育局表示，由於地震活動持續，一間鄰近火山區的學校已經停課。<br />\n夏威夷縣長辦公室早前發出聲明，指三級政府正為火山可能爆發作準備，包括物色庇護所、動員警方和其他保安人員，以確保居民安全，並責令道路工作人員確保疏散路線暢通。"},{"pid":"1ef328e78374d8209ee87695dd12e9ad496d3e3a","tid":652803,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58151178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58151178&d=VW6EldCff5cYGF6oeE%2BgtTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6a02698e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180504%2F58151178&h=b2a089c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180504/58151178</a><br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷基拉韋厄火山（Kilauea Volcano）爆發，有住宅區的地面裂縫湧出熔岩，當局要求區內所有居民撤離，連同附近受影響的區域共有1萬名民眾要緊急疏散。美國地質調查局亦已將當地的火山警告級別提升至最高。<br />\n<br />\n約有1,500人居住的萊拉妮區（Leilani Estates、音譯），有街道的裂縫噴出岩漿，情況嚇人。居民馬索（Ikaika Marzo）指熔岩如噴泉般湧出，有45米高、覆蓋範圍有182米闊，更傳出類似噴射引擎啟動的聲音。<br />\n另一位居民奧蘇納（Jeremiah Osuna）就指，熔岩令不少樹木焚毀，形容是一道火場：「就似是將一堆石頭放入乾衣機，再調較至最高速運轉模式。你可以嗅到有硫磺味、樹木或雜物被燒著的氣味。」<br />\n美國地質調查局稱收到區內其他地方出現新地面裂縫的報告，同樣有噴出熱氣及岩漿，又指火山周圍的地區有可能會被熔岩覆蓋，尤以萊拉妮區的風險最高，因為無從預測何處會冒出新裂縫。<br />\n當局已向萊拉妮區所有居民發出強制撤離令，連同住宅區所在的普納（Puna），共有1萬人要疏散。"},{"pid":"0a86053b34fe65d40f3172f7f3ada9cadd9766cf","tid":652803,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7vSFRSGIkoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7vSFRSGIkoU&d=VW6EldCff5cYGF6oeE%2BgtTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3553f2fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7vSFRSGIkoU</a>"},{"pid":"9ce0d0b1021088d958ee71007481a1b37ecd0e86","tid":652803,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"Mola street <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}